I"),<p>This page lists the sources where you can find the vacancies for PhD and other academic positions. I created this list for myself as I have been looking for open PhD positions, but I decided to put it online so that other interested people can benefit from it.</p>

<p>I am interested in the positions related to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Cosmology, Astrophysics, Cosmic Rays, Machine Learning, High Performance Computing, Simulations, Data Analysis, Data Science, etc.</li>
</ul>

<p>Please feel free to write to me at: <a href="mailto:dyskun@yahoo.com">dyskun@yahoo.com</a> to say Thanks or if you know about some position related to above mentioned fields that’s not listed here.</p>

